Reconfigure Sales Analytics

To reconfigure an existing app, navigate to CRM Analytics Studio and open the app. Click the Reconfigure app link below the app name.
Review carefully as reconfiguring overwrites app customizations.
Complete the app creation process described in Create and Share Sales Analytics.

If you delete your app, CRM Analytics doesnâ€™t retain the answers you selected when you created that version of the app, and you have to start the creation process all over again. 

Important:
Reconfiguring your app gets rid of dashboard customizations.
It also deletes actions you enable, or changes to security settings and dashboard colors and labels.
